OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FThe UK's Supreme Court will give a
OL,7,Flong-waited judgment in relation to
OL,8,Fthe car finance commission saga on
OL,9,FFriday.
OL,11,FIt is set to bring clarity over how
OL,12,Fthe law should be applied to motor
OL,13,Ffinance arrangements following a Court
OL,14,Fof Appeal decision last October.
OL,16,FThe ruling will have much wider
OL,17,Framifications for the industry, and
OL,18,Fthe financial services sector, and
OL,19,Fcould mean millions of motorists are
OL,20,Fdue compensation as a result.
