OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FHere, the PA news agency looks at the
OL,7,Fpotential impact of the decision on
OL,8,Fconsumers, lenders, and the wider car
OL,9,Ffinance market.
OL,11,F` What is the background to the court
OL,12,Fcase?
OL,14,FThe Supreme Court ` the UK's highest
OL,15,Fcourt ` is considering an appeal
OL,16,Fagainst a Court of Appeal ruling made
OL,17,Fin October last year, relating to
OL,18,Fthree claimants who had each bought
OL,19,Fcars on credit.
