OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FIn each case, the car dealer made a
OL,7,Fprofit on the sale of the car but also
OL,8,Freceived a commission from the lender
OL,9,Ffor introducing the business to them `
OL,10,Fwhich the three claimants argued they
OL,11,Fdid not know about.
OL,13,FThe Court of Appeal found that
OL,14,F"secret" commission payments, as part
OL,15,Fof finance arrangements made before
OL,16,F2021 without the motorist's fully
OL,17,Finformed consent, were unlawful.
OL,19,FThe lenders, FirstRand Bank and Close
OL,20,FBrothers, are challenging that
OL,21,Fdecision.
