OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,F` Why is this court case so important?
OL,8,FWayne Gibbard, who leads the
OL,9,Fautomotive finance practice at law
OL,10,Ffirm Shoosmiths, said Friday's Supreme
OL,11,FCourt decision will be "absolutely
OL,12,Ffundamental to what happens next" for
OL,13,Fthe sector.
OL,15,FHe said it will inform the scale of
OL,16,Fpotential compensation for customers,
OL,17,Fwhich will be overseen by the UK's
OL,18,FFinancial Conduct Authority (FCA).
