OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FThe FCA previously said that, if it
OL,7,Fthinks there was widespread harm to
OL,8,Fconsumers as a result of commission
OL,9,Fpayments, then it could set up an
OL,10,Findustry-wide redress scheme.
OL,12,FIt said it will confirm within six
OL,13,Fweeks of the Supreme Court judgment
OL,14,Fwhether it is planning to launch such
OL,15,Fa scheme.
OL,17,FMr Gibbard stressed that this response
OL,18,Fwill be particularly important going
OL,19,Fforward.
