OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FHe said: "People can make an informed
OL,7,Fdecision ` the query is around their
OL,8,Fharm, have they been mis-sold
OL,9,Fsomething?
OL,11,F"And I think that's been absent in the
OL,12,Fconversation."
OL,14,F` What does it mean for consumers?
OL,16,FIf Supreme Court judges side with the
OL,17,Fclaimants then it could mean that many
OL,18,Fpeople who took out a car loan before
OL,19,F2021 may be due a payout, although it
OL,20,Fis difficult to say at this point how
OL,21,Fmany.
