OL,3,CCar finance: What is the court case
OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FIf it sides with the lenders, then it
OL,7,Fis likely to significantly limit the
OL,8,Fscope of potential payouts to
OL,9,Fmotorists.
OL,11,FHowever, the FCA is still looking at
OL,12,Fcompensation for potential mis-selling
OL,13,Fof some types of motor finance
OL,14,Farrangements ` known as discretionary
OL,15,Fcommission arrangements (DCAs) ` so
OL,16,Fthis could go ahead regardless.
