OL,4,Cabout and what does it mean for me?
OL,6,FIf the FCA decides to proceed with a
OL,7,Fredress scheme, it is likely to
OL,8,Fclarify what type of motor finance
OL,9,Farrangements it applies to ` and
OL,10,Fpotentially include all deals where
OL,11,Fpeople were not told clearly enough,
OL,12,For at all, that the car dealer was
OL,13,Freceiving commission.
OL,15,FA scheme is intended to be simpler for
OL,16,Fconsumers than making a direct
OL,17,Fcomplaint to providers.
