OL,6,FThe watchdog said it would expect
OL,7,F"fewer consumers to rely on a claims
OL,8,Fmanagement company, meaning they would
OL,9,Fkeep all of any compensation they
OL,10,Freceive" and would be "more orderly
OL,11,Fand efficient for firms than a
OL,12,Fcomplaint-led approach".
OL,14,FMahesh Vara, a legal director for
OL,15,FShoosmiths, said a decision that
OL,16,Fsecret commission payments were
OL,17,Funlawful would "naturally be a boon to
OL,18,Fclaimants firms and consumers".
